{
  "stem": "18397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- but the guys, the rest of it, not the Jews, they didn't have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had some-- some brushes, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they used to clean it with the-- with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- I had a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had a shoe brush, you know, to-- to brush the shoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, of course, I was doing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we started together, you know, put the-- the dirt maybe so much there together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to pull it in the pail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one of the guys took some dirt, put it over my head, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had the brush in my hand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I broke his nose.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the first thing right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I had respect.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I became one of the boys, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There had a lot of respect for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they didn't put me in jail for breaking a nose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was really [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But it was before you would swear to the-- to the constitutionals or somebody over there that you obey all the laws.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then-- then they can take you to the-- to the court and put you in jail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I was lucky they didn't put me in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, everybody had a horse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] is a-- a gypsy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What happened to everybody?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the horses to the war, we put us-- they put us in train, five or six horses in a train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one guy who had to clean them, you know, from the-- and they took us down to Poland, you know, down.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
